Import our car file that we created

import print title 

define the main function

ask for the user's name, color car, seating, and max speed

go to the get_info function

create a variable for the user's choice on whether to go, stop, or exit

create a while true loop

if speed choice is a, accelerate
if speed choice is b, brake
if speed choice is s, stop
if speed choice is e, exit and break
if speed is more than the max speed, print an error
any other letter/characrer, break

call the main function